Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,离发射还有15分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,甘草 预定稍微推迟
